STATE EX REL. KOUNS
v.
GREENE 2019-0408 Supreme Court of Ohio. June 5, 2019

CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

O'Connor, C.J., and Kennedy, French, Fischer, DeWine, Donnelly, and Stewart, JJ., concur.
